            <div class="panel">
                <ul>
                    <li>Visionary thinking: decades ahead, anticipate trends.</li>
                    <li>Crisis management: handle stress and uncertainty like a pro.</li>
                    <li>Negotiation with global-level players.</li>
                    <li>Emotional control & energy mastery.</li>
                    <li>Reinvention: adapt to market and personal growth.</li>
                    <li>Legacy mindset: beyond wealth, beyond fame, lasting impact.</li>
                </ul>
